(43, 21, 6, 58, 2, 6, 9, NULL, 'Divine Provision and Human Response', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine provision in both passages. In John 21:6, the disciples receive an abundant catch of fish through obedience, while Hebrews 2:6-9 emphasizes God''s care for humanity and the glory bestowed upon Jesus, who fulfills God''s plan for salvation.', 'theme', 0.307, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
