(43, 21, 13, 43, 21, 9, 9, NULL, 'Connection of Bread and Fish', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of bread and fish, highlighting a shared meal that Jesus provides for his disciples. This connection illustrates the continuity of Jesus'' care and sustenance for them after his resurrection.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
